title: Tenticle plant
text: Seeing I've logged alot about hte various animals I thought I would take some tiem ot log about some local fauna.
This spore like plant with large tenticles, while nasty looking, was in fact very soft, almost silky to touch.
It was carbon based, with no toxins detected I couldn't resist eating a little bit.
Tasted like it looked, wont be eating that again.
